es athleticism and body control.\", \"from\": 3791, \"to\": 3857, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The first istechnique\", \"from\": 3791, \"to\": 3812}, {\"ngram\": \"athleticism\", \"from\": 3828, \"to\": 3839}, {\"ngram\": \"body control\", \"from\": 3844, \"to\": 3856}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The second isvocabulary, or the variety of a dancer's moves.\", \"from\": 3858, \"to\": 3918, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The second isvocabulary\", \"from\": 3858, \"to\": 3881}, {\"ngram\": \"the variety\", \"from\": 3886, \"to\": 3897}, {\"ngram\": \"a dancer's moves\", \"from\": 3901, \"to\": 3917}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Third isexecution,in which the higher-scoring competitor, according to the World DanceSport Federation rulebook, \\\"demonstrates a greater ability to perform their moves distinctly and to a high degree of cleanliness, minimizing slips, falls, or crashes.\\\"\", \"from\": 3919, \"to\": 4172, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3994, \"end\": 4021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"World DanceSport Federation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Third isexecution\", \"from\": 3919, \"to\": 3936}, {\"ngram\": \"the higher-scoring competitor\", \"from\": 3946, \"to\": 3975}, {\"ngram\": \"a greater ability\", \"from\": 4046, \"to\": 4063}, {\"ngram\": \"their moves\", \"from\": 4075, \"to\": 4086}, {\"ngram\": \"a high degree\", \"from\": 4105, \"to\": 4118}, {\"ngram\": \"cleanliness\", \"from\": 4122, \"to\": 4133}, {\"ngram\": \"slips\", \"from\": 4146, \"to\": 4151}, {\"ngram\": \"crashes\", \"from\": 4163, \"to\": 4170}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then there ismusicality,for which the judges are eyeing rhythms and movements synchronized to the music, and finally,originality,or spontaneity, personality, and innovation.\", \"from\": 4173, \"to\": 4346, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Then there ismusicality\", \"from\": 4173, \"to\": 4196}, {\"ngram\": \"the judges\", \"from\": 4207, \"to\": 4217}, {\"ngram\": \"rhythms\", \"from\": 4229, \"to\": 4236}, {\"ngram\": \"movements\", \"from\": 4241, \"to\": 4250}, {\"ngram\": \"the music\", \"from\": 4267, \"to\": 4276}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement Whoever dances better, in the eyes of the majority of the judges, wins the round.\", \"from\": 4348, \"to\": 4444, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Whoever\", \"from\": 4362, \"to\": 4369}, {\"ngram\": \"the eyes\", \"from\": 4388, \"to\": 4396}, {\"ngram\": \"the majority\", \"from\": 4400, \"to\": 4412}, {\"ngram\": \"the judges\", \"from\": 4416, \"to\": 4426}, {\"ngram\": \"the round\", \"from\": 4433, \"to\": 4442}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The best-of-three-round battles continue through the gold-medal match, which will take place a little after 3:20 p.m. E.T.\", \"from\": 4445, \"to\": 4567, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"-round\", \"from\": 4462, \"to\": 4468}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold-medal match\", \"from\": 4494, \"to\": 4514}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 4532, \"to\": 4537}, {\"ngram\": \"E.T.\", \"from\": 4563, \"to\": 4567}]}, {\"sentence\": \"on August 9 (B-girls) and August 10 (B-boys).\", \"from\": 4568, \"to\": 4613, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 4571, \"to\": 4577}, {\"ngram\": \"(B-girls\", \"from\": 4580, \"to\": 4588}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 4594, \"to\": 4600}, {\"ngram\": \"B\", \"from\": 4605, \"to\": 4606}, {\"ngram\": \"-boys\", \"from\": 4606, \"to\": 4611}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A brief primer on the lingo:top rockis the foot-shuffling and arm-moving a breaker does while standing up.Down rockis the action on the floor.\", \"from\": 4615, \"to\": 4757, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A brief